---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Boxing Timer Champ">
  <main class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-500 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-elegant-text-secondary mb-8">Last updated: April 4, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-elegant-text-primary mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
            At Boxing Timer Champ, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data when you use our website and mobile application.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-elegant-text-primary mb-4">Data Collection and Usage</h2>
          <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
            We collect information that you voluntarily provide to us when using our services, as well as data collected automatically through analytics and tracking tools. This may include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-elegant-text-secondary">
            <li>Information you submit when contacting us</li>
            <li>Usage data from our timer application</li>
            <li>Technical details about your device and browser</li>
            <li>Aggregated analytics data collected through services like Google Analytics and Hotjar, which help us understand how visitors interact with our website and improve user experience</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
            These services may use cookies or similar technologies to collect anonymous data. You can manage your cookie preferences at any time via our cookie consent banner.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-elegant-text-primary mb-4">Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
            We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. Your data is stored securely and only accessed by authorized personnel.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-elegant-text-primary mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-elegant-text-secondary mb-4">
            You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. You can also object to the processing of your data or request data portability.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
